And 'Localization, by compartments' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Proximal enthesis' radio button is enabled
And 'Prox.myotendinous junction' radio button is enabled
And 'Proximal 1/3' radio button is enabled
And 'Middle 1/3' radio button is enabled
And 'Muscle lesion' checkbox is enabled

And 'Fatty infiltration' checkbox is enabled
And 'Muscular atrophy' checkbox is enabled
And 'Apophysitis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Fascial laceration' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Muscle lesion' checkbox
Then 'Muscular Edema' radio button is enabled
And 'Minor partial muscle tear (type IIIa)' radio button is enabled
And 'Moderate partial muscle tear (type IIIb)' radio button is enabled
And '(Sub)total muscle tear/tendinous avulsion (type IV)' radio button is enabled


When I select 'Minor partial muscle tear (type IIIa)' radio button
Then 'Rupture diameter < 5 mm' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Minor partial muscle tear (type IIIa)' radio button
Then 'Cross diameter of rupture â‰¥ 5 mm' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Minor partial muscle tear (type IIIa)' radio button
Then 'Retraction' input field is enabled
And 'Wavy appearance of the fibers' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bony avulsion' checkbox is enabled
And 'Intracortical edema' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Muscular atrophy' checkbox
Then 'Moderate' radio button is enabled
And 'Advanced' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Fascial laceration' checkbox
Then 'Muscle herniation' checkbox is enabled
